issue.title: Stream line
issue.body:
Pull request did the following:

- Removed a bunch of useless training data.
- Reorganized folder structure. 
- Commented and tieded up code.
- Wrote a quick function that takes a .csv file of data and outputs a classifier. Sets up the framework for doing all the training in MATLAB. 
- Updated README and other such misc items.
